section.def:
existing register (原有註冊名冊), in relation to a profession, means the
                    register for that profession kept under section 10(1) of the
                    pre-amended Ordinance;

existing registrant (原有註冊人) means a person whose name was entered in
                    an existing register immediately before the commencement date in accordance with
                        section 13 of the pre-amended Ordinance;
